  "text": "In the particular case of AN associated with insulinoma, since the tumor is well circumscribed and surgically curable, the skin lesion may completely disappear when the removal of the insulinoma is achieved [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . There has even been a report of complete remission of AN after the partial pancreatectomy for the HAIR-AN syndrome (86).",
